sequenceDiagram
participant Developer
participant CoreSystems as Core Systems Server (PMS, MMS)
participant CICD as CI/CD Pipeline
participant ContainerRegistry as Container Registry
participant DeploymentOrchestrator as Deployment Orchestrator
participant Factories

Developer ->> CoreSystems: Implement new feature
Developer ->> CICD: Commit new update
CICD ->> ContainerRegistry: Build and push Docker image
DeploymentOrchestrator ->> ContainerRegistry: Fetch latest image version
DeploymentOrchestrator ->> CoreSystems: Deploy new version to Core Systems server
CoreSystems --> Developer: Deployment confirmed
Factories ->> CoreSystems: Continue normal data exchange (no direct deployment)
